### Gradient Descent

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Model
    participant Loss

    Model->>Loss: Compute ŷ = Xβ
    Loss->>Loss: MSE = (1/n)||y - ŷ||²
    Loss->>Model: Gradient ∇β = -(2/n) Xᵀ(y - ŷ)
    Model->>Model: β ← β - η·∇β
    Note over Model,Loss: Repeat until convergence
```

