## 18. Full Comparison & Cheat Sheet

### Regularisation Methods

| | OLS | Ridge | Lasso | Elastic Net |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Penalty** | None | L2 | L1 | L1 + L2 |
| **Sparse?** | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ | ✅ |
| **Closed form** | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| **Multicollinearity** | ❌ fails | ✅ great | ⚠️ picks one | ✅ groups |
| **Feature selection** | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ | ✅ |
| **Tune** | — | $\lambda$ | $\lambda$ | $\lambda, \alpha$ |

### SVM Variants

| Variant | Task | Key Params |
|---|---|---|
| **Hard-Margin SVM** | Binary (separable) | — |
| **Soft-Margin SVM** | Binary (general) | $C$ |
| **SVM + RBF** | Non-linear classification | $C, \gamma$ |
| **SVR** | Regression | $C, \varepsilon$ |

### Essential Equations

$$\hat{\boldsymbol{\beta}}_\text{OLS} = (\mathbf{X}^\top\mathbf{X})^{-1}\mathbf{X}^\top\mathbf{y}$$

$$\hat{\boldsymbol{\beta}}_\text{ridge} = (\mathbf{X}^\top\mathbf{X} + \lambda\mathbf{I})^{-1}\mathbf{X}^\top\mathbf{y}$$

$$J_\text{lasso} = \|\mathbf{y} - \mathbf{X}\boldsymbol{\beta}\|^2 + \lambda\|\boldsymbol{\beta}\|_1$$

$$K_\text{RBF}(\mathbf{x}_i, \mathbf{x}_j) = \exp\!\left(-\gamma\|\mathbf{x}_i - \mathbf{x}_j\|^2\right)$$

